or and mystery writer from Gifu. He is married to voice actress Ao Takahashi and is the CEO of Black Ship.\n\nAfter gratudating from Aoni Juku Tokyo School 18th term he joined Production Baobab. In 2003, he made his voice actor debut as Kyo in the TV anime E's Otherwise. He belonged to Production Baobab until May 2011. In June of the same year he joined Axl One. On January 5, 2017, he reported his marriage to Ao Takahashi on his blog. On March 31, 2018, he left Axl One to establish, together with Jun Fukuyama, their own agency: Black Ship.","name":"Shinnosuke Tachibana","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"立花慎之介，日本男性聲優，出身於岐阜縣。過去曾隸屬於 Production baobab，在2011年6月1日移籍於 AXL ONE，並於2018年3月31日離開，移籍到與福山潤一同創立的BLACK SHIP。在2017年1月1日與聲優高梁碧結婚。","name":"立花慎之介","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"타치바나 신노스케","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"ชินโนสึเกะ ทาจิบานะ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Šinnosuke Tačibana","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"立花慎之介（日语：立花 慎之介／たちばな しんのすけ Tachibana Shinnosuke，1978年4月26日—），日本男性声优，出身于岐阜县。过去曾隶属于Production baobab，在2011年6月1日移籍于AXL ONE，并于2018年3月31日离开，移籍到与福山润一同创立的BLACK SHIP。在2017年1月1日与声优高梁碧结婚。","name":"立花慎之介","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Shinnosuke Tachibana","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"立花慎之介，日本男性聲優，出身於岐阜縣。過去曾隸屬於 Production baobab，在 2011 年 6 月 1 日移籍於 AXL ONE，並於 2018 年 3 月 31 日離開，移籍到與福山潤一同創立的 BLACK SHIP。在 2017 年 1 月 1 日與聲優高梁碧結婚。","name":"立花慎之介","primary":fa